rows.label: qev026003_MSG0021
rows.name:
Go on, go on. Give those welkin auravises a taste of
the weapon I lent you, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0022
rows.name:
Once we prove to NLA that Ma-non tech is the best
around, we're sure to seal all kinds of amazing deals,
aren't we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0001
rows.name:
Excellent work, right? I've heard reports on your results
in using our latest weapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0002
rows.name:
Would be so good as to return it to me now, please?
Thanks. Many many thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0003
rows.name:
You're as impressive as I'd heard. And I'm a genius for
scouting you to head our field-marketing efforts, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0004
rows.name:
The parts where you pretended to struggle and/or
bleed really added a sense of drama, you know?
You're kind of a ham. But the good kind, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0005
rows.name:
Overcome the direst of all dire odds with a weapon
from Candid & Credible at your side![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0006
rows.name: ...The ad copy practically writes itself, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0007
rows.name:
What? Why, yes! This IS where you can find the
unbeatable new weapon you've heard about![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0008
rows.name:
You're quite the savvy customer, right? This model here
is the weapon that slew a welkin auravis in the blink
of an eye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0009
rows.name:
Ah, and a welcome to you, too! Welcome one and all
to Candid & Credible House of Fine Wares, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0010
rows.name:
Ride the cutting edge with the most advanced tech in
all of space and time, okay? Because when your life
could be gone, you better trust Ma-non![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0011
rows.name:
Incredible! I never dreamed this ad campaign would
work so well! Or so quickly, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0012
rows.name: It's all thanks to to to you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0013
rows.name:
I'll be sure to come to you straightaway if I ever need
help again, okay? I hope we can be very very good
business partners for a long time, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0014
rows.name:
Because at Candid & Credible, integrity comes free!
...Er, right? It's totally free? Like, included?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0015
rows.name:
You keep our business booming, we'll make your
enemies go BOOM! It's back scratching all around at
your friendly neighborhood Candid & Credible![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0016
rows.name:
Come to us for all your needs, from paper napkins to
interstellar generation ships, yes? Everything is in stock
here at Candid & Credible![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0023
rows.name:
Go on, go on. Tear through those 10 iron femina
suids lickety-split with that weapon I lent you, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0024
rows.name:
Once we prove to NLA that Ma-non tech is the best
around, we're sure to seal all kinds of amazing deals,
aren't we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0017
rows.name:
You're quite the savvy customer, I see? Yes, this very
model is the weapon that cut down a whole line of
iron femina suids in one fell swoop.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0018
rows.name:
Excellent work, right? I've heard reports on your results
in using our latest weapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0019
rows.name:
Would be so good as to return it to me now, please?
Thanks. Many many thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev026003_MSG0020
rows.name:
Ah, I'm afraid I can't take it while it's still equipped.
...Er, forgive me, yes? No offense?[ST:wait ]
